    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you mention the \"environmental necessity\" part, how much of that is seen as an objective goal vs. just a policy preference? Like, is there actually a consensus on whether these pricing schemes are the most effective way to hit climate targets, or is it more of a specific ideological approach?",
